name: MOST ELEGANT MONKEY EVER
description: The Most Elegant Monkey Ever is a revived and reimagined meme project designed to stand out in the crypto space. Originally abandoned at a $13k market cap, this project has been taken over with a vision to create the biggest meme phenomenon, combining humour, community engagement, and real-world utility. We're not just a meme; we're building a movement that brings together innovation and fun, paving the way for a vibrant and dynamic ecosystem.
